527
00:40:38,813 --> 00:40:41,822
 Because you'll want to keep your position. 

528
00:40:51,012 --> 00:40:55,022
Hey. If I want to go independent as Soonyang Financial Group,

529
00:40:55,022 --> 00:40:57,622
