530
00:40:57,622 --> 00:41:01,193
Is it liquidating Chairman Jin Young Ki's shares in the financial affiliates?

531
00:41:01,193 --> 00:41:03,792
You are half right and half wrong.

532
00:41:03,792 --> 00:41:06,033
How can I buy all of Young Ki hyungnim's shares with the money I have right now?

533
00:41:06,033 --> 00:41:07,093
No, it's impossible.

534
00:41:07,093 --> 00:41:11,633
I need a cash cow to earn me money until the separation is complete.

535
00:41:11,633 --> 00:41:17,733
So is the cash cow slash golden goose you're thinking of inside Soonyang Group?

536
00:41:17,733 --> 00:41:19,443
Soonyang Card.

537
00:41:19,443 --> 00:41:22,422
Nothing beats a card company in cash flows.

538
00:41:22,422 --> 00:41:24,983
So I'm going to buy Soonyang Card first.

539
00:41:24,983 --> 00:41:26,812
Do you think Do Jun will sell it?

540
00:41:26,812 --> 00:41:31,483
If it's a cash cow even you have eyes on, I doubt Do Jun will put it out for sale.

541
00:41:31,483 --> 00:41:33,993
I think he'll sell it.

542
00:41:33,993 --> 00:41:35,962
You'll sell it?

543
00:41:37,063 --> 00:41:40,232
You'll sell Sooyang Card to me?

544
00:41:40,232 --> 00:41:41,762
Yes.

545
00:41:50,472 --> 00:41:54,212
It hasn't been that long since you took over Soonyang Card.

546
00:41:54,212 --> 00:41:58,282
Thanks to Cheongwadae lifting all regulations to improve the domestic market

547
00:41:58,282 --> 00:42:03,383
before the presidential election, the growth of card companies has been steep.

548
00:42:03,383 --> 00:42:07,422
But you're going to hand it over to me?

549
00:42:08,222 --> 00:42:09,423
Why?

550
00:42:09,423 --> 00:42:12,873
You're going to buy it at a high price, aren't you?

551
00:42:18,432 --> 00:42:23,102
Honestly, even the holding company establishment went down the drain.

552
00:42:23,102 --> 00:42:27,803
So I don't think you, who's quick with numbers and has a great sense of reality,

553
00:42:27,803 --> 00:42:32,713
will waste time clinging to becoming the head of Soonyang Group.

554
00:42:32,713 --> 00:42:34,582
If I were in your shoes, Uncle Dong Ki,

555
00:42:34,582 --> 00:42:40,523
I would go independent from Soonyang Group and consider a separate Financial group.

556
00:42:40,523 --> 00:42:47,222
To do so, I thought you would need Soonyang Card that could bring in cash at any time,

557
00:42:47,222 --> 00:42:50,763
in order to take care of the shares.

558
00:42:50,763 --> 00:42:52,503
You.

559
00:42:53,273 --> 00:42:59,343
Couldn't you, Do Jun, separate Soonyang Financial Group and manage it?

560
00:42:59,343 --> 00:43:05,013
You already have Soonyang Card, the cash cow.

561
00:43:05,013 --> 00:43:07,153
Me,

562
00:43:07,982 --> 00:43:12,823
who got branded an evil child blinded by legacy at the shareholders' meeting?

563
00:43:13,553 --> 00:43:18,523
Will Soonyang Group's board of directors, united with loyalties for Grandfather,

564
00:43:18,523 --> 00:43:23,992
choose me as the head and CEO of Soonyang Group?

565
00:43:23,992 --> 00:43:25,033
I don't think so.

566
00:43:25,033 --> 00:43:26,973
Even so,

567
00:43:26,973 --> 00:43:33,243
you foil the plan for the holding company establishment your grandfather had worked so hard on.

568
00:43:33,243 --> 00:43:36,073
When you are his grandson?

569
00:43:40,653 --> 00:43:44,503
Because I threw away my dream of succeeding to Soonyang Group.

570
00:43:46,722 --> 00:43:49,723
I'm going to return to my original place.

571
00:43:49,723 --> 00:43:53,142
As Miracle's investment specialist, Jin Do Jun.

572
00:43:54,463 --> 00:43:59,503
So what's most important to me right now isn't Soonyang Group but money, Uncle Dong Ki.

573
00:43:59,503 --> 00:44:05,503
And as you already know, the more money, the better.

574
00:44:17,483 --> 00:44:19,123
It looked like he was going to ask

575
00:44:19,123 --> 00:44:21,423
for more than 800 billion won  ($800M)  for selling Soonyang Card.

576
00:44:21,423 --> 00:44:23,062
What do you think, Director Baek?

577
00:44:23,062 --> 00:44:25,292
Should I go for it or not?

578
00:44:25,292 --> 00:44:27,093
More than that, Vice-Chairman Jin.

579
00:44:27,093 --> 00:44:29,563
In 2003, the Year of the Black Sheep,

580
00:44:29,563 --> 00:44:35,063
Vice-Chairman Jin Young Ki's new year's fortune will change.

581
00:44:35,063 --> 00:44:36,303
So what?

582
00:44:36,303 --> 00:44:38,773
Vice-Chairman Jin Young Ki has a fate eulmokilju.

583
00:44:38,773 --> 00:44:42,542
He has been in the shade of a large tree, unable to make his way.

584
00:44:42,542 --> 00:44:44,443
But starting in the Year of the Black Sheep,

585
00:44:44,443 --> 00:44:48,413
