586
00:44:48,413 --> 00:44:50,523
What's this all about, Director Baek?

587
00:44:50,523 --> 00:44:51,553
Hold on.

588
00:44:51,553 --> 00:44:52,852
Out of all the Year of the Black Sheep,

589
00:44:52,852 --> 00:44:58,610
the yin and yang of the Five-elements will attract each other the most this year.

590
00:44:58,610 --> 00:45:03,532
And in all probability, there might be a storm like the IMF crisis next year.

591
00:45:03,532 --> 00:45:04,662
Let's be prepared.

592
00:45:04,662 --> 00:45:06,303
What about my fortune?

593
00:45:06,303 --> 00:45:09,542
Should I buy Soonyang Card? Does it say I should?

594
00:45:09,542 --> 00:45:11,202
Father.

595
00:45:11,202 --> 00:45:16,112
Your fortune next year is mugyejihwa. It's full of fire.

596
00:45:16,112 --> 00:45:19,483
It meets metal and blazes.

597
00:45:20,582 --> 00:45:25,153
It looks like you're in luck with the finance industry.

598
00:45:25,153 --> 00:45:27,122
What are you two doing?

599
00:45:27,122 --> 00:45:30,523
How can you decide to buy Soonyang Card like this?

600
00:45:30,523 --> 00:45:32,332
You need the opinions of experts.

601
00:45:32,332 --> 00:45:34,533
Director Baek is an expert.

602
00:45:34,533 --> 00:45:37,062
He's an analyst who was formerly an accountant.

603
00:45:37,062 --> 00:45:40,432
Ye Jun, you said that Do Jun won't sell Soonyang Card.

604
00:45:40,432 --> 00:45:44,173
But look. Everything is unfolding according to his words.

605
00:45:44,173 --> 00:45:47,642
Eight hundred billion won  ($800M)  is too much money to leave up to luck.

606
00:45:47,642 --> 00:45:53,043
I know how good Director Baek is because we've worked together all along.

607
00:45:54,753 --> 00:46:00,723
You're admitting that you've been running the company like this to this day.

608
00:46:02,093 --> 00:46:05,293
- Does the Internal auditor know? 
 - Jin Ye Jun!

609
00:46:05,293 --> 00:46:08,193
You punk. Get out.

610
00:46:08,193 --> 00:46:12,202
You're the only one who doesn't qualify to be here now.

611
00:46:21,012 --> 00:46:22,982
Vice-Chairman Jin, do you remember?

612
00:46:22,982 --> 00:46:25,483
When the US stock market crashed after the September 11 attack,

613
00:46:25,483 --> 00:46:27,312
if you went with my advice,

614
00:46:27,312 --> 00:46:32,622
you wouldn't have lost Soonyang Investment to Miracle Investment.

615
00:46:32,622 --> 00:46:34,753
Make a call.

616
00:46:35,423 --> 00:46:38,323
I'm buying Soonyang Card.

617
00:46:38,323 --> 00:46:42,592
Do you really think Soonyang Card is only worth 800 billion won  ($800M) ?

618
00:46:46,403 --> 00:46:48,832
Okay, then.

619
00:46:48,832 --> 00:46:52,322
Let's negotiate the details when we meet next time.

620
00:46:53,213 --> 00:46:55,412
Yes, give me a call.

621
00:47:06,752 --> 00:47:10,123
You're selling Soonyang Card to whom?

622
00:47:10,892 --> 00:47:12,992
Is it Uncle Dong Ki?

623
00:47:15,502 --> 00:47:18,452
He can't answer, which means I'm right, Father.

624
00:47:25,443 --> 00:47:27,043
Hey.

625
00:47:27,943 --> 00:47:29,212
What brings you here today?

626
00:47:29,212 --> 00:47:32,512
He'd like to go with you on his way to work.

627
00:47:43,792 --> 00:47:47,693
I hear Do Jun will sell Soonyang Card.

628
00:47:48,463 --> 00:47:52,502
I heard that you stepped in as the new owner.

629
00:47:52,502 --> 00:47:54,373
What are you saying?

630
00:47:54,373 --> 00:47:57,742
Who said that? Do Jun?

631
00:47:58,602 --> 00:48:02,542
Do you still believe what Do Jun says?

632
00:48:02,542 --> 00:48:04,613
It's fine if it isn't you.

633
00:48:05,682 --> 00:48:10,282
I thought a go-getter like you was trying to break away as a financial group,

634
00:48:10,282 --> 00:48:12,952
so I had to hurry over from the morning.

635
00:48:13,952 --> 00:48:18,363
This is unsettling. I should use this chance to purchase Soonyang Card.

636
00:48:18,363 --> 00:48:19,992
You're going to buy Soonyang Card?

637
00:48:19,992 --> 00:48:23,863
That way, there would be zero chance for the affiliates to break away.

638
00:48:23,863 --> 00:48:27,003
I also don't want to be mistaken about you over a rumor,

639
00:48:27,003 --> 00:48:29,102
which will lead me down the evil path.

640
00:48:29,102 --> 00:48:31,652
Nothing good can come from that between us.

641
00:48:33,113 --> 00:48:36,412
Dong Ki, don't forget.

642
00:48:36,412 --> 00:48:39,282
It's only meaningful when we are united.

643
00:48:39,282 --> 00:48:43,122
Both Soonyang and us brothers.

644
00:48:53,492 --> 00:48:55,733
Hey, Jin Do Jun!

645
00:49:02,003 --> 00:49:04,202
What do you want?

646
00:49:04,202 --> 00:49:08,472
Are you trying to pit Hyungnim Young Ki against me over Soonyang Card?

647
00:49:08,472 --> 00:49:11,182
I would never do that.

648
00:49:11,182 --> 00:49:14,153
I was always taught to stop fights and strike a bargain.

649
00:49:14,153 --> 00:49:16,412
What?

650
00:49:16,412 --> 00:49:21,153
Thanks to that, Uncle Dong Ki, you ran over here at this hour.

651
00:49:22,963 --> 00:49:26,032
In that case, why don't we start the proper negotiation?

652
00:49:26,032 --> 00:49:27,792
Shall we?

653
00:49:28,593 --> 00:49:34,603
You offered 800 billion won  ($800M)  for Soonyang Card, so let's start the bargain at twice that price.

654
00:49:34,603 --> 00:49:36,602
Twice?

655
00:49:37,303 --> 00:49:39,653
I want 1.6 trillion won  ($1.6B). 

656
00:49:39,653 --> 00:49:43,642
That's the price for Soonyang Card offered by Jeongsimjae.

657
00:49:48,613 --> 00:49:50,753
If you need more time to think...

658
00:49:50,753 --> 00:49:53,193
Wait! Can I pay half and half?

659
00:49:53,193 --> 00:49:57,023
I'll transfer 800 billion won  ($800M)  today and the rest of 800 billion next time.

660
00:49:57,023 --> 00:50:00,633
Okay, sure. As long as the collateral is solid.

661
00:50:00,633 --> 00:50:04,743
Are you demanding the shares of the financial affiliates?

662
00:50:04,743 --> 00:50:05,632
Hey, you punk!

663
00:50:05,632 --> 00:50:08,872
I'll take Soonyang Corporation's shares as collateral.

664
00:50:08,872 --> 00:50:10,972
Two percent of your share.

665
00:50:11,702 --> 00:50:14,252
I don't care for the financial group.

666
00:50:14,252 --> 00:50:16,542
Don't worry about it.

667
00:50:16,542 --> 00:50:17,982
Then why?

668
00:50:17,982 --> 00:50:20,953
Among all of your assets including real estate,

669
00:50:20,953 --> 00:50:24,053
isn't that the most valuable as collateral?

670
00:50:24,053 --> 00:50:26,253
The shares of the Corporation.

671
00:50:28,323 --> 00:50:30,573
I'll get it ready and call you.

672
00:50:31,463 --> 00:50:32,732
I do have one more condition.

673
00:50:32,732 --> 00:50:34,962
Good grief, what?

674
00:50:39,332 --> 00:50:41,903
I need some untraceable money,

675
00:50:41,903 --> 00:50:45,103
apart from the sale price for Soonyang Card.

676
00:50:45,912 --> 00:50:47,512
A slush fund?

677
00:50:51,443 --> 00:50:53,813
It truly is the high season.

678
00:50:53,813 --> 00:50:56,182
Even an investment company like Miracle is

679
00:50:56,182 --> 00:50:59,992
preparing political funds for the presidential election?

680
00:50:59,992 --> 00:51:02,762
According to CEO Oh Se Hyeon, in the US,

681
00:51:02,762 --> 00:51:05,892
Wall Street is the funding behind the presidential election.

682
00:51:05,892 --> 00:51:10,042
That 45 percent of political funds come from Wall Street.

683
00:51:10,042 --> 00:51:12,102
It means the main industry has changed.

684
00:51:12,102 --> 00:51:13,103
From manufacturing to finance.

685
00:51:13,103 --> 00:51:15,233
Do you know

686
00:51:15,233 --> 00:51:20,843
to whom and how you should transfer the money to make sure there's no trouble later?

687
00:51:20,843 --> 00:51:22,213
Trouble?

688
00:51:22,213 --> 00:51:23,713
You need to bribe them

689
00:51:23,713 --> 00:51:27,512
without a delivery mistake and not letting anyone else know.

690
00:51:27,512 --> 00:51:30,803
Well, I guess your father doesn't have what it takes

691
00:51:30,803 --> 00:51:33,892
to teach you something like that.

692
00:51:33,892 --> 00:51:36,423
And CEO Oh may know a lot about Wall Street,

693
00:51:36,423 --> 00:51:40,023
but he's probably a layman when it comes to Yeouido*. 
