00:52:52,432 --> 00:52:54,832
His daughter is something, too.

712
00:52:54,832 --> 00:52:57,343
She's in a different league compared to other tycoons' kids.

713
00:52:57,343 --> 00:53:00,742
You said she passionately volunteers in third-world countries, right?

