00:53:00,742 --> 00:53:04,912
She only volunteers in countries where she can evade taxes.

715
00:53:04,912 --> 00:53:09,613
Thanks to her, we made ten billion won  ($10M)  in cash slush fund without any trouble.

716
00:53:09,613 --> 00:53:14,292
The fruit of someone else's work is always the most delicious.

