741
00:54:23,642 --> 00:54:28,233
So go tell your brothers that we should lie low for a while as the wind blows.

742
00:54:28,233 --> 00:54:31,832
Go tell them yourself.

743
00:54:32,702 --> 00:54:36,503
They lost 30 billion won  ($30M)  at your word!

744
00:54:39,273 --> 00:54:42,373
Goodness, look who this is.

745
00:54:43,843 --> 00:54:47,453
Yes, congratulations, Mr. President.

746
00:54:47,453 --> 00:54:51,122
Yes, right. I should have called first.

747
00:54:51,122 --> 00:54:52,922
Yes.

748
00:54:52,922 --> 00:54:55,453
Yes. Pardon?

749
00:54:57,022 --> 00:54:58,962
Me?

750
00:55:00,332 --> 00:55:04,632
Yes, I'll do my best if you leave me to it.

751
00:55:04,632 --> 00:55:06,503
Yes, I understand. Thank you.

752
00:55:06,503 --> 00:55:09,373
Yes. Goodbye.

